Package net.caspervg.jgaf.step

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Breeder<O>
    Provides a way to breed (a part of) the population based on given arguments
    Creator<O>
    Provides a way to create an initial population based on the arguments
    Crosser<O>
    Provides a way to perform crossover
    Fitter<O>
    Provides a way to calculate the fitness of an organism
    Killer<O>
    Provides a way to kill organisms in the population
    Mutator<O>
    Provides a way to mutate an organism
    Selector<O>  
    StepProvider<O>
    Provides strategies for all the steps in a genetic algorithm.
